  "title": "Technical Officer (East/Up $3k/ No Exp ok!)",
  "description": "<p><strong>The Opportunity</strong></p><ul><li>Opportunity to be part of a global semiconductor MNC</li><li>Shift: Monday to Friday, 7:00am – 4:30pm & 4pm-1:30am. </li><li>Location: East, Changi/Tampines</li><li>12 months (contract extension/ conversion subject to performance and business directions)</li><li>Salary up to $3k+ !</li><li>Shift allowance provided!</li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li>Work in a cleanroom and operate testing/assembly equipment</li><li>Perform routine maintenance, troubleshooting, and basic repairs</li><li>Set up, calibrate, and prepare equipment for daily use</li><li>Read and understand simple electro‑mechanical diagrams and drawings</li><li>Take accurate measurements and support other tasks as needed</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>NITEC, Higher NITEC, or Diploma in any related engineering fields</li><li>Candidates with or without prior experience are welcome to apply as training will be provided </li></ul><p><strong>Next Step</strong></p><p>Prepare your updated resume, send to the following email: <a href=\"mailto:amelia.lau@adecco.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">amelia.lau@adecco.com </a></p><p>*Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted*<br /></p><p>Amelia Lau An Qi</p><p>Direct Line: +65 6697 7987<br />EA License No: 91C2918<br />Personnel Registration Number: R1987023</p>",
